# File naming

All new files must use **kebab-case** (lowercase words separated by hyphens).

```text
✅ episode-card.tsx
✅ tokens.stories.tsx
✅ studio-welcome.mdx
✅ use-media-query.ts

❌ EpisodeCard.tsx
❌ StudioWelcome.mdx   (use studio-welcome.mdx)
❌ Icons.stories.tsx   (use icons.stories.tsx)
❌ useMediaQuery.ts
```

Applies to source, stories, styles, and docs. React component **exports** stay PascalCase (`EpisodeCard`); only the **filename** is kebab-case.

When renaming existing PascalCase files, prefer kebab-case in the same change if you are already touching that file.
